Legacy of Evil is the sixth studio album by Norwegian symphonic black metal band Limbonic Art. CD Universe[1] Released by Nocturnal Art Productions and marketed and distributed by Candlelight Records. Recorded at MOF studios 2007 by Morfeus. Mastered by Tom Kvalsvoll at Strype Audio. Produced and Mixed by Limbonic Art. All Lyrics written by Daemon.[2]
